{"tid":1073833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Shake 薯條太嘈 比隻蝗投訴","createTime":"2019-03-23T03:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T03:56:19.000Z","uid":244102,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b07714356cf2eb7b08d31254af5e11644871b7c6","tid":1073833,"uid":244102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T03:37:55.000Z","msg":"琴日喺清水灣大學間m 記同同事食lunch<br />\n咁我同事好勇敢咁試新出既出前一丁麻油味shake shake 粉（沒有最難食 只有更難食）<br />\n<br />\n咁佢就正常咁shake啦 突然有隻蝗蟲 同我同事講 話佢製造噪音 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">騷擾佢傾電話[/i]</span></strong> 叫我個同事靜啲<br />\n<br />\n而我地望佢 一個人霸左成張枱 無買任何野食 坐足半個鐘喺度傾電話🖕🏻<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來大陸人心目中嘅m 記唔係食shake shake 薯條 而係用嚟傾電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6d1cde03dcf988c2e60b7018a90ca8b62404e2","tid":1073833,"uid":49690,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T03:39:09.000Z","msg":"上黎開Post不如shake大力啲"},{"pid":"7f726eb346cf5a3205d22189c96a693a513de584","tid":1073833,"uid":19421,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"你唔係咁樣就俾佢收咗皮呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"d12ad194034dddcd790bb3de3892b5dc1c30f4ed","tid":1073833,"uid":93078,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T03:39:21.000Z","msg":"人多都縮？"},{"pid":"1fd1ac331d40b5bd271cbc0c363626933c6da2ba","tid":1073833,"uid":121249,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T03:41:28.000Z","msg":"淆閪牙 你咁多人"},{"pid":"b28b0f1c63c6c65a5d563d0a5d25dd5f6006b9be","tid":1073833,"uid":244102,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T03:41:47.000Z","msg":"跟住我地shake 另一包 專登大聲啲<br />\n另一個同事話佢痴撚線😂"},{"pid":"c899b89fbc05650dab33ed96f638ead993638328","tid":1073833,"uid":119767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T03:42:44.000Z","msg":"學d正苦廢老話齋<br />\n唔滿意嘅咪叫佢走唔好坐係度囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji